channel.description:

I tried a couple of source and it say in english : its impossible to find principale class Jframe[url=http://postimg.org/image/eptsyl4l5/][img]http://s12.postimg.org/eptsyl4l5/Jframe.jpg[/img][/url]....Please some 1 please help me

item.title: Need Help!
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

It can’t find your jframe class. Meaning the run.bat is looking for Jframe.class in a directory it isn’t in. You need to edit it so it can find the appropriate file. That’s as much as I can say since I don’t know what your directory’s and file structure looks like…
